<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Daniel Pipes</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Daniel_pipes_bw.jpg" class="image" title="Daniel pipes bw.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/65/Daniel_pipes_bw.jpg/230px-Daniel_pipes_bw.jpg" width="230" height="320" border="0" /></a><br /></td>
