<th>Born</th>
<td>September 9, 1949 <span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1949-09-09</span>)</span> <span class="noprint">(age&#160;59)</span><br />
<a href="/wiki/Boston" title="Boston">Boston</a>, <a href="/wiki/Massachusetts" title="Massachusetts">Massachusetts</a></td>
